{"about_the_game":"<strong>Holy Heroes</strong> is a cooperative game for one to four players, sharing the same screen on a single computer via keyboard and controllers (type PS4, Xbox and generics). Players can choose from 9 distinct hero classes (Knight, Dwarf, Barbarian, Wizard, Cleric, Ninja, Necromancer, Paladin, and Archer) to explore diverse floors and biomes in pursuit of main or side missions. The game features 9 spheres of power (Air, Water, Earth, Fire, Life, Death, Magic, Mind, and Nature) that influence monsters, enchantments, and enhancements, along with a variety of items to equip and use.<br><br>In addition to multiple floors to explore with increasing difficulty, the game includes traps, weather changes, portals, guardians, lever systems, and other elements that constantly demand players' attention, keeping them engaged.<br><br>\u2022\tExplore procedurally generated worlds, always different.<br>\u2022\tAcquire weapons, armor, shields, accessories, and more.<br>\u2022\tDiscover your strategy by freely choosing your spells.<br>\u2022\tForge and reforge items to always be prepared for any adversity.<br>\u2022\tLearn special skills and acquire professions.<br>\u2022\tComplete side quests while exploring the main mission's labyrinths.<br>\u2022\tExperience day and night cycles, facing storms, fogs, and other challenges.<br>\u2022\tAvoid traps and discover secret passages.<br>\u2022\tUpon leveling up, enhance your heroes by deciding where to allocate points.<br>\u2022\tNavigate through over twenty floors with various branches and biomes.<br>\u2022\tEach floor may contain multiple levels.<br>\u2022\tEncounter diverse monsters per biome and floor, with many creatures to discover in each unique world.<br>\u2022\tPlay alone or with up to 3 friends by your side.<br>\u2022\tShare gold and experience with your group, if desired.<br>\u2022\tConfigure quick actions with up to 6 game commands.<br>\u2022\tBecome a Sacred Hero!<br>\u2022\tFor a challenging experience, we recommend Nightmare mode.<br>\u2022\tBe careful, as playing with only one life is fatal!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Nobody Forgets the First Key","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/ed933e6c2a8a7edf428d46fb79c4656674efd766.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Keys","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/b1a6dd799ab25e64c46dbb77f0538217a68a8bc6.jpg"},{"name":"Instant Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/bc1a6483cd5415447fa150880bea510b3cfc6160.jpg"},{"name":"The Floor Is Mine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/9b271268aedc6122a8a5b3add95dd1448ab1f021.jpg"},{"name":"Five Hundred of Chaos","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/50cd318f8960f40dede348fb694054b01e06276b.jpg"},{"name":"Relentless Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/33b4d3e580421c33c7b1980413a95c6f35a13b16.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Devastation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/6fc4e4ec2ee2e7e71c47bbe2511d7434541a5359.jpg"},{"name":"The Fall of the Goblark","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/047caec96d6001687d96781ff5d6934c093c786a.jpg"},{"name":"End of the Furygob","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/e90c6b966e4c52a111993d4cb2d71c03a797166b.jpg"},{"name":"Colossal Slime, Colossal Victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3107270/fcd043bc2ce959372f278f291e75593c00a45119.jpg"}],"total":100},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738434464","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107270/p